{
  "video_id": "wQ0NNmo42-A",
  "title": "Bionic Symbiotics | Nigel Ackland | TEDxAcademy",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16976.0,
      "end_time": 18127.0,
      "text": "For somebody like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18151.0,
      "end_time": 22182.0,
      "text": "to be speaking here is truly an honour and a privilege."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23710.0,
      "end_time": 26729.0,
      "text": "So, Niki, Katerina - thank you, and thanks to the TEDxAcademy."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26753.0,
      "end_time": 27904.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27928.0,
      "end_time": 32974.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33792.0,
      "end_time": 37141.0,
      "text": "The next few minutes might be slightly different"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37165.0,
      "end_time": 38474.0,
      "text": "to what you&#39;re expecting."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39553.0,
      "end_time": 42620.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have a presentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42870.0,
      "end_time": 46436.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m not an expert in evolution or technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47470.0,
      "end_time": 51583.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Nigel, I&#39;m just an ordinary man with an extraordinary arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 52447.0,
      "end_time": 56628.0,
      "text": "My story starts in September 2006."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 58164.0,
      "end_time": 62655.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m at work, I&#39;m cleaning out the drum of an industrial blender."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 63923.0,
      "end_time": 65504.0,
      "text": "The drum starts to spin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 66465.0,
      "end_time": 67980.0,
      "text": "I get dragged inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 68672.0,
      "end_time": 70274.0,
      "text": "and my arm becomes trapped."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 71843.0,
      "end_time": 73560.0,
      "text": "The drum stops for a few seconds."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73584.0,
      "end_time": 75765.0,
      "text": "And then, like a pendulum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75789.0,
      "end_time": 77273.0,
      "text": "it changes direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 78692.0,
      "end_time": 82377.0,
      "text": "I feel my arm being squeezed, then crushed."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 83171.0,
      "end_time": 86654.0,
      "text": "And I hear the bones snap before it finally stops."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87572.0,
      "end_time": 88996.0,
      "text": "So I wait for help."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 90511.0,
      "end_time": 93366.0,
      "text": "Thirty minutes later I&#39;m still trapped"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 93391.0,
      "end_time": 94816.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m getting desperate."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 96840.0,
      "end_time": 99207.0,
      "text": "The rescue teams, they can&#39;t get to me safely."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 101370.0,
      "end_time": 103183.0,
      "text": "Somebody threw a screwdriver to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 104343.0,
      "end_time": 107984.0,
      "text": "I caught the screwdriver and dug myself free."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 109587.0,
      "end_time": 112985.0,
      "text": "Once I&#39;d climbed out of the drum, the paramedics took over."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 115420.0,
      "end_time": 119613.0,
      "text": "A week later, the nurses are removing my bandages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 119637.0,
      "end_time": 121731.0,
      "text": "the doctors have come to have a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 122631.0,
      "end_time": 126760.0,
      "text": "My left leg has been cut from my hip to my knee"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 126784.0,
      "end_time": 130365.0,
      "text": "and a large piece of my leg has been cut away"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 130389.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131893.0,
      "text": "and wrapped around my arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 133557.0,
      "end_time": 138617.0,
      "text": "My hand is a mess - there are scars, stitches everywhere,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 138641.0,
      "end_time": 142536.0,
      "text": "with this big lump of leg wrapped around my forearm."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 145189.0,
      "end_time": 148596.0,
      "text": "The doctors explain that putting me back together again"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 148621.0,
      "end_time": 150644.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t going to be quick or easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 151367.0,
      "end_time": 153595.0,
      "text": "I face up to 10 years of treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 154271.0,
      "end_time": 156326.0,
      "text": "and there are no guarantees of success."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 158227.0,
      "end_time": 162710.0,
      "text": "So I turned to the Internet, looking for answers, making notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 162734.0,
      "end_time": 165210.0,
      "text": "trying to find out exactly what I&#39;m facing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 165234.0,
      "end_time": 167992.0,
      "text": "how it could affect me and what my options are."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 169963.0,
      "end_time": 173826.0,
      "text": "Six months later, my arm is still not healing."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 175220.0,
      "end_time": 177780.0,
      "text": "I take my notes to a surgeon."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 177883.0,
      "end_time": 181627.0,
      "text": "I ask him to read them as if he was reading about himself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 182826.0,
      "end_time": 186780.0,
      "text": "and then explain to me the benefits of keeping my arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 187861.0,
      "end_time": 190316.0,
      "text": "Four days later I became an amputee."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 192204.0,
      "end_time": 194666.0,
      "text": "Now, during a planned amputation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 194690.0,
      "end_time": 199138.0,
      "text": "a surgeon will leave the patient with the longest stump possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 200240.0,
      "end_time": 204652.0,
      "text": "It makes, apparently, prosthetics more comfortable to wear."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 205864.0,
      "end_time": 207605.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s standard procedure."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 209416.0,
      "end_time": 213454.0,
      "text": "So, following standard procedure, they left me the longest stump possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 214281.0,
      "end_time": 218376.0,
      "text": "To achieve it, they cut through the thickest part of my graft."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 219548.0,
      "end_time": 223742.0,
      "text": "So instead of my arm tapering, it gets wider."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 225298.0,
      "end_time": 227583.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know it at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 227607.0,
      "end_time": 231209.0,
      "text": "but the shape of my stump was going to cause me a lot of problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 231967.0,
      "end_time": 234524.0,
      "text": "All I wanted to do was to get my life back."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 236388.0,
      "end_time": 238919.0,
      "text": "My company said I&#39;d get the best treatment possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 239268.0,
      "end_time": 240784.0,
      "text": "They had good insurance."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 241679.0,
      "end_time": 243632.0,
      "text": "A bionic arm? No problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 244540.0,
      "end_time": 246500.0,
      "text": "Back to work, simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 247485.0,
      "end_time": 248857.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 248881.0,
      "end_time": 252640.0,
      "text": "Some small print in the insurance policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 253300.0,
      "end_time": 256878.0,
      "text": "meant that instead of the treatment I was told to expect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 256903.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258632.00000000003,
      "text": "I was sent to the NHS."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 261389.0,
      "end_time": 264979.0,
      "text": "“Standard procedure” is a three-stage plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 265300.0,
      "end_time": 266830.0,
      "text": "and they don&#39;t do bionic hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 269219.0,
      "end_time": 271979.0,
      "text": "Stage one, they call it a passive limb."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 272963.0,
      "end_time": 275872.0,
      "text": "It looks like a hand, it&#39;s got no function."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 276465.0,
      "end_time": 277965.0,
      "text": "Mine didn&#39;t fit very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 278608.0,
      "end_time": 281217.0,
      "text": "It was five centimeters longer than my left arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 283636.0,
      "end_time": 287240.0,
      "text": "Six months later I moved on to stage two."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 287480.0,
      "end_time": 290331.0,
      "text": "Stage two is a body-powered system."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 292539.0,
      "end_time": 293777.0,
      "text": "(Sighs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 293802.0,
      "end_time": 295924.0,
      "text": "Again, mine didn&#39;t fit too well."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 296686.0,
      "end_time": 299984.0,
      "text": "It was uncomfortable to wear and painful to use."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 300889.0,
      "end_time": 305587.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a hook, developed over 100 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 306285.0,
      "end_time": 310269.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s powered by a piece of string and a rubber band."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 313623.0,
      "end_time": 317117.0,
      "text": "The end of 2008, I&#39;m back in hospital again."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 318839.0,
      "end_time": 323690.0,
      "text": "Constantly trying to jam my flared stump into a tapered socket"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 323714.0,
      "end_time": 328356.0,
      "text": "has been causing pressure sores, infection and a lot of pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 329699.0,
      "end_time": 331295.0,
      "text": "They amputate again."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 333950.0,
      "end_time": 336303.0,
      "text": "2009, well, that starts quietly."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 337198.0,
      "end_time": 341667.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m finally clear of infection and it&#39;s time to start again."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 343619.0,
      "end_time": 347301.0,
      "text": "Physically, life is a challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 349150.0,
      "end_time": 351748.0,
      "text": "I used to be the provider for my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 353158.0,
      "end_time": 356868.0,
      "text": "But the strong, fit, active Nigel that I used to see in the mirror -"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 356892.0,
      "end_time": 358454.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s disappeared."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 360962.0,
      "end_time": 363494.0,
      "text": "My left arm is now damaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 363518.0,
      "end_time": 366539.0,
      "text": "My weight, about 120 kilos."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 368258.0,
      "end_time": 370313.0,
      "text": "I need help just to get dressed."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 372149.0,
      "end_time": 375593.0,
      "text": "Psychologically, I&#39;m in a dark place."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 376901.0,
      "end_time": 378800.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve moved into my spare room."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 379691.0,
      "end_time": 382601.0,
      "text": "Nighttimes, they&#39;re for the nightmares."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 384980.0,
      "end_time": 388610.0,
      "text": "I wake up, soaked with sweat or screaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 389821.0,
      "end_time": 392823.0,
      "text": "Daytimes are for the mood swings -"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 392847.0,
      "end_time": 395671.0,
      "text": "the massive highs, the crashing lows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 395696.0,
      "end_time": 397656.0,
      "text": "fears, self-doubts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 398322.0,
      "end_time": 400380.0,
      "text": "frustration and anger -"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 402165.0,
      "end_time": 405530.0,
      "text": "the sudden, raging anger"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 405770.0,
      "end_time": 409128.0,
      "text": "that I quite often unfairly take out on my wife and my son."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 414715.0,
      "end_time": 416150.0,
      "text": "I lost my place."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 416886.0,
      "end_time": 418677.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 418701.0,
      "end_time": 420280.0,
      "text": "One second."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 420520.0,
      "end_time": 422305.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 426000.0,
      "end_time": 427278.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m so sorry."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 430407.0,
      "end_time": 433328.0,
      "text": "Talking about my wife always leaves me speechless."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 433352.0,
      "end_time": 435349.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 437542.0,
      "end_time": 440585.0,
      "text": "About the - sorry. There we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 440610.0,
      "end_time": 444126.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 449705.0,
      "end_time": 451596.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll try and win this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 453423.0,
      "end_time": 455882.0,
      "text": "About this time I also notice a change"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 455906.0,
      "end_time": 458659.0,
      "text": "in other people&#39;s attitudes towards me."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 459925.0,
      "end_time": 462379.0,
      "text": "Strangers often avoid me."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 463147.0,
      "end_time": 467156.0,
      "text": "Very rarely do people make eye contact or start a conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 467573.0,
      "end_time": 473950.0,
      "text": "They stop and stare, sometimes with pity, fear, disgust."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 474854.0,
      "end_time": 476873.0,
      "text": "Some will point and laugh."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 477670.0,
      "end_time": 479354.0,
      "text": "Some will just yell insults."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 480814.0,
      "end_time": 482104.0,
      "text": "I stop going out."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 482852.0,
      "end_time": 484522.0,
      "text": "I become withdrawn."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 486450.0,
      "end_time": 490950.0,
      "text": "I start shutting myself away from everybody,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 490119.0,
      "end_time": 492380.0,
      "text": "sometimes for days on end."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 492404.0,
      "end_time": 494459.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll sit outside, in my garage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 495691.0,
      "end_time": 497808.0,
      "text": "just me and my demons."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 499733.0,
      "end_time": 502885.0,
      "text": "Now 2009, yes, it started quietly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 502909.0,
      "end_time": 504408.0,
      "text": "but it ended with a bang."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 505876.0,
      "end_time": 509695.0,
      "text": "Bang! Heart Attack. Dead. Game Over."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 510988.0,
      "end_time": 512484.0,
      "text": "Or so I thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 513409.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518139.99999999994,
      "text": "They put six stents into my heart and sent me off to cardio rehab."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 520302.0,
      "end_time": 522330.0,
      "text": "So two years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 523392.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527129.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been using a myoelectric Greifer."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 528295.0,
      "end_time": 530716.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been using it for a while and I&#39;m used to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 530740.0,
      "end_time": 534699.0,
      "text": "And I can finally afford to get this socket custom-made."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 536422.0,
      "end_time": 538446.0,
      "text": "One day I get a call from the prosthetist."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 538470.0,
      "end_time": 540818.0,
      "text": "He said a company called RSLSteeper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 540842.0,
      "end_time": 544374.0,
      "text": "they have a new prosthetic hand, they want someone to test it."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 546182.0,
      "end_time": 547618.0,
      "text": "He mentioned me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 548459.0,
      "end_time": 552340.0,
      "text": "and a short while later, I became the first person in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 552365.0,
      "end_time": 555589.0,
      "text": "to start long-term testing of the bebionic v3."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 556939.0,
      "end_time": 558267.0,
      "text": "So, here&#39;s my arm."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 558753.0,
      "end_time": 560641.0,
      "text": "And briefly, this is what it does:"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 561559.0,
      "end_time": 564158.0,
      "text": "I have three basic pieces."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 564182.0,
      "end_time": 565801.0,
      "text": "I have my socket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 567255.0,
      "end_time": 570117.0,
      "text": "which is the most important piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 570975.0,
      "end_time": 572485.0,
      "text": "If this isn&#39;t comfortable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 572509.0,
      "end_time": 575682.0,
      "text": "if you can&#39;t wear this all day without pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 576348.0,
      "end_time": 578722.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t matter how good this piece is -"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 578746.0,
      "end_time": 582590.0,
      "text": "it will stay in the cupboard, unused."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 583842.0,
      "end_time": 587539.0,
      "text": "Next, I have the most useful piece; it&#39;s my wrist."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 588344.0,
      "end_time": 593754.0,
      "text": "It allows me not to use my left hand to change the position."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 594609.0,
      "end_time": 595833.0,
      "text": "It is useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 596714.0,
      "end_time": 599169.0,
      "text": "And then, we have the coolest bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 600480.0,
      "end_time": 602630.0,
      "text": "Now, my socket, like I said, is custom-made."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 602654.0,
      "end_time": 604431.0,
      "text": "I have two electrodes."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 604455.0,
      "end_time": 608764.0,
      "text": "One sits against my skin here and one sits against my skin here."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 609828.0,
      "end_time": 613247.0,
      "text": "And all I need to do is make the muscles contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 614117.0,
      "end_time": 617425.0,
      "text": "So if I imagine I&#39;m opening a can of beer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 618807.0,
      "end_time": 619957.0,
      "text": "it opens."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 620441.0,
      "end_time": 622475.0,
      "text": "If I imagine I&#39;m squeezing a ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 623440.0,
      "end_time": 624194.0,
      "text": "it closes."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 625101.0,
      "end_time": 626879.0,
      "text": "And if there are any guys out there"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 626903.0,
      "end_time": 629318.0,
      "text": "who can&#39;t open a beer and squeeze your balls -"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 629342.0,
      "end_time": 631247.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 631271.0,
      "end_time": 636699.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 640400.0,
      "end_time": 642330.0,
      "text": "maybe this one is not for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 643472.0,
      "end_time": 646668.0,
      "text": "I have eight different grip patterns on this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 646692.0,
      "end_time": 650434.0,
      "text": "So, this is my basic grab. I can change grip."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 650935.0,
      "end_time": 654870.0,
      "text": "They call this power grip; I call it handshake grip."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 655849.0,
      "end_time": 658992.0,
      "text": "I can move the thumb. It&#39;s two-position and it&#39;s manual."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 659455.0,
      "end_time": 664271.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s manual and it knocks about 10,000 pounds off the price."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 665170.0,
      "end_time": 666647.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s it."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 667142.0,
      "end_time": 668929.0,
      "text": "So now, I can read my books."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 669384.0,
      "end_time": 672312.0,
      "text": "If I want to do anything on the keyboard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 672336.0,
      "end_time": 674157.0,
      "text": "I can change the grip."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 674181.0,
      "end_time": 678368.0,
      "text": "If it&#39;s in the wrong place, the useful wrist comes into play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 678392.0,
      "end_time": 679607.0,
      "text": "and now I can type."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 680687.0,
      "end_time": 682326.0,
      "text": "If I&#39;m using my mouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 683660.0,
      "end_time": 685517.0,
      "text": "I press the magic button on the back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 685541.0,
      "end_time": 687764.0,
      "text": "single click, double click."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 688185.0,
      "end_time": 691590.0,
      "text": "The latest software has drag-and-drop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 691615.0,
      "end_time": 692796.0,
      "text": "which is pretty cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 693644.0,
      "end_time": 695669.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 696308.0,
      "end_time": 699551.0,
      "text": "If I want to freak children out -"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 699575.0,
      "end_time": 701511.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 705754.0,
      "end_time": 707145.0,
      "text": "I sort of do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 707169.0,
      "end_time": 708961.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 709338.0,
      "end_time": 712510.0,
      "text": "And if that doesn&#39;t work, we just carry on."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 712534.0,
      "end_time": 714912.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 714936.0,
      "end_time": 720453.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 723495.0,
      "end_time": 725850.0,
      "text": "That will usually get their attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 725874.0,
      "end_time": 728983.0,
      "text": "but I just let them know it&#39;s actually OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 731600.0,
      "end_time": 734467.0,
      "text": "The reaction I get from people in the street"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 734491.0,
      "end_time": 736564.0,
      "text": "to whatever prosthetic I&#39;ve worn"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 736588.0,
      "end_time": 739650.0,
      "text": "has always had a very direct and very powerful effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 739674.0,
      "end_time": 742198.0,
      "text": "on the way I felt as a human being."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 743842.0,
      "end_time": 747324.0,
      "text": "Since I&#39;ve had this, the effect on my life has been extraordinary."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 748548.0,
      "end_time": 753874.0,
      "text": "People still stop and stare, but it&#39;s not with pity or fear."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 754730.0,
      "end_time": 758247.0,
      "text": "People tend to laugh with me instead of at me."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 759855.0,
      "end_time": 762708.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll talk and I&#39;ll show off."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 763498.0,
      "end_time": 767270.0,
      "text": "The best thing - I call it the bebionic effect -"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 767510.0,
      "end_time": 770579.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s when we shake hands, people smile."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 770603.0,
      "end_time": 772516.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a genuine smile."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 772540.0,
      "end_time": 777540.0,
      "text": "And I see that handshake and that smile as a sign of acceptance"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 777564.0,
      "end_time": 778865.0,
      "text": "for who I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 781260.0,
      "end_time": 786165.0,
      "text": "Just before I got this, I was speaking with a psychiatrist."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 788325.0,
      "end_time": 793577.0,
      "text": "He said to me, \"Where do you see yourself in a year or so?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 795597.0,
      "end_time": 796918.0,
      "text": "I thought about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 798230.0,
      "end_time": 800220.0,
      "text": "“I’ll be in the countryside,” I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 800460.0,
      "end_time": 801754.0,
      "text": "“sitting in my car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 803318.0,
      "end_time": 806254.0,
      "text": "with a hosepipe attached to the exhaust.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 807769.0,
      "end_time": 810510.0,
      "text": "I wasn&#39;t trying to be dramatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 810750.0,
      "end_time": 813550.0,
      "text": "I just couldn&#39;t see a future for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 814787.0,
      "end_time": 816405.0,
      "text": "I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 817854.0,
      "end_time": 819402.0,
      "text": "A year or so later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 820720.0,
      "end_time": 824758.0,
      "text": "I stood on stage for the first time in my life and shared my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 826350.0,
      "end_time": 830102.0,
      "text": "This hasn&#39;t cured my phantom pains."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 831155.0,
      "end_time": 835867.0,
      "text": "It hasn&#39;t stopped the nightmares and it hasn&#39;t stopped the flashbacks."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 837110.0,
      "end_time": 840510.0,
      "text": "But it has convinced me that life-changing"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 840750.0,
      "end_time": 842494.0,
      "text": "does not have to be life-ending."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 843280.0,
      "end_time": 848632.0,
      "text": "That with the right support, the right care, the right prosthetics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 849734.0,
      "end_time": 854834.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a chance for us to have a new and different life."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 855855.0,
      "end_time": 857986.0,
      "text": "A chance to stand on our own two feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 859636.0,
      "end_time": 863834.0,
      "text": "Like I say, a year or so ago, I told my story for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 864636.0,
      "end_time": 868736.0,
      "text": "It seemed that my new and different life had started then."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 869994.0,
      "end_time": 872521.0,
      "text": "And whether you realize it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 873585.0,
      "end_time": 876351.0,
      "text": "every single one of you has been part"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 876375.0,
      "end_time": 878445.0,
      "text": "of my new and different life."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 878827.0,
      "end_time": 880121.0,
      "text": "And I thank you for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 880145.0,
      "end_time": 886630.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 894419.0,
      "end_time": 899441.0,
      "text": "And before I go, I urge you, please -"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 900346.0,
      "end_time": 903916.0,
      "text": "go and be part of someone else&#39;s new and different life."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 903940.0,
      "end_time": 905910.0,
      "text": "(Greek) Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 905115.0,
      "end_time": 907786.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 907810.0,
      "end_time": 908984.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 909900.0,
      "end_time": 911852.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 911876.0,
      "end_time": 913260.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 913510.0,
      "end_time": 915592.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 915616.0,
      "end_time": 917720.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 917960.0,
      "end_time": 923363.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}